<template>
  <!-- No changes to template section -->
</template>

<script>
import { ref } from 'vue'
import { useRouter } from 'vue-router'

export default {
  setup() {
    const router = useRouter()
    const handleEdit = (row) => {
      if (row.healthAssessmentStatus !== '完成') {
        router.push(`/assessment/health/${row.assessmentId}`)
      } else {
        router.push(`/assessment/care/${row.assessmentId}`)
      }
    }

    return {
      handleEdit
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style>
  /* No changes to style section */
</style>
